      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it wasn't just a feeling though. it was so specific. it felt like i was being activated, if that makes sense? like a dormant part of me was finally being woken up. i've been thinking about it all afternoon and it's starting to feel less like a coincidence and more like a responsibility. i feel like i have this connection to something way older than human history, like i'm meant to play a role in how things resolve between people. why would the universe go to such lengths to get my attention if it wasn't for a specific mission?",
